r />\n所以結論係佢派錢嘅話 好大機會會通脹"},{"pid":"b5fc0226d8bf603b7afe722e62abca9604727085","tid":914010,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf82e6b4e33f63b1dfff5468b29fc66c535b9bd","tid":914010,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"印銀紙會通脹, 派錢會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"如果李嘉誠燒哂自己d錢<br />\n一定會通縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2a4a8c95bea6ed2077b7a90b5d2ef48e204158","tid":914010,"uid":14371,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"d錢最後又會入返誠哥袋"},{"pid":"ba652373a7d8583eeb8516d1d66da4aeab31b9e8","tid":914010,"uid":137732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d2a4a8c95bea6ed2077b7a90b5d2ef48e204158","tid":914010,"uid":14371,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"d錢最後又會入返誠哥袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:53:10.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021be27429faa42347e12917eaee1b1116112559","tid":914010,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"會，<br />\n市場流動資金增加左就自然通脹，<br />\n唔係長期都可以係通脹，通脹就係社會流動資金增加<br />\n因為呢舊錢放係李嘉誠到大部份佢都唔會拎出黎洗"},{"pid":"97215d35ef3b1896fffd9d61985f82d021f31f5e","tid":914010,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇啲港豬係即刻用咗佢、買資產定儲喺銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8546f60cfb2cc440d4c91630edffcc435ae995","tid":914010,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n澳門年年派錢, 造成的通脹有幾多?<br />\n對比香港, 又差幾多?"},{"pid":"e52885e57038961dea4e8866a92431f51d93a429","tid":914010,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"我唔敢講100%唔會，但就算會通脹都係輕微到你感覺唔到。<br />\n<br />\n通脹因素不外乎，錢供應多咗(鳩印錢)，或流通量大咗。<br />\n<br />\n錢本身係李嘉誠嘅，所以錢供應冇多到。<br />\n<br />\n咁流通嚟講，每人多咗幾萬蚊做得啲乜，你會因為咁食多兩餐？買多格車？所以消費品基本嘅係唔會變<br />\n<br />\n最有可能係 iPhone or ps4 會有炒價，多咗班中小學生去買，港女買下啲袋或化妝品，但香港基數大，好多人嚟走水貨，所以港女買多咗都唔會有大影響。<br />\n<br />\n而最大可能係股票升咗，俾個股市吸曬啲錢。"}]}